'''''My Little Pony Crystal Princess: The Runaway Rainbow''''' is an [[Adventure game|adventure]]/[[puzzle video game]] developed by [[Webfoot Technologies]] and published by [[THQ]] under license from Hasbro. It was released for [[Game Boy Advance]] on September 13, 2006 in North America. The game recreates events from the film of the same title, featuring mini-games and puzzles.{{Citation needed |date=September 2014}}

